column5: I pointed to two old drunks sitting across the bar from us and told my friend  "That's us in 10 years". He said "That's a mirror, dumb arse"
lol....your on a roll this week Ron...  ...stay on the lighter side of life...its more fun then the other side
Hey what can I say..Glad to be of a service!
Did you hear about the Beauty Contest in Newfoundland?  Guess who won....
Ya got me??? this should be good tho..

"He's saying we're going the wrong way"...."  how can that be, he doesn't even know where we're going"....DA....
